---++ <nop>TWikiSiteTools
d78 2
a79 2
TWikiSiteTools include utilities for navigation and for monitoriing web and site-wide activity. WebPreferences can be individually configured. 
	* You are currently in the *[[%WEB%.%HOMETOPIC%][%WEB%]]* web.
a80 12
<form action="%SCRIPTURLPATH%/search%SCRIPTSUFFIX%/%WEB%/">
	* WebSearch: Full text search of this web<br>
	  <input type="text" name="search" size="32" /> <input type="submit" value="Search" /> &nbsp;&nbsp; (extended options in WebSearch)
	* WebChanges: Display recent input on the this web
	* WebIndex: List all web topics in alphabetical order. See also the faster WebTopicList
	* %NOTIFYTOPIC%: Subscribe to an email alert linking to the most recently changed topics in this web 
	* %STATISTICSTOPIC%: View access statistics for this web
</form>
	* %WEBPREFSTOPIC%: Preference settings for the this web 
	* %WIKIPREFSTOPIC%: %WIKITOOLNAME% site-wide preferences
	* The %TWIKIWEB%.SiteMap: A color-coded directory of available webs that can be easily included on any page _(below)_
		* The [[%TWIKIWEB%.%HOMETOPIC%][%WEB%]] web is coded light orange for quick identification.
